commentText: Provides the {@link Setting setting configuration} for each internal realm type._This excludes the ReservedRealm, as it cannot be configured dynamically.
codeText: public static Set<Setting.AffixSetting<?>> getSettings() {_        Set<Setting.AffixSetting<?>> set = new HashSet<>()__        set.addAll(FileRealmSettings.getSettings())__        set.addAll(NativeRealmSettings.getSettings())__        set.addAll(LdapRealmSettings.getSettings(LdapRealmSettings.AD_TYPE))__        set.addAll(LdapRealmSettings.getSettings(LdapRealmSettings.LDAP_TYPE))__        set.addAll(PkiRealmSettings.getSettings())__        set.addAll(SamlRealmSettings.getSettings())__        return Collections.unmodifiableSet(set)__    }
